{"tid":125941,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完arrival，想問主角個女最尾點？主角同個女係河邊傾緊咩？","createTime":"2017-02-19T03:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T17:09:41.000Z","uid":66822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f50499592134eac0127b2ccd2d9b57d39f105db3","tid":125941,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:11:23.000Z","msg":"外星人走左，大概發生左幾件事<br />\n<br />\n１８月後　　慶祝酒會大陸佬畀電話同遺言<br />\n之後　　　　主角結婚　然後生女<br />\n之後　　　　個女畫幅畫同玩泥膠<br />\n之後　　　　主角同女係河邊（唔知點解鷹眼走左，個女病左）<br />\n之後　　　　個女死左？？<br />\n<br />\n點解個女病左，鷹眼會走佬既，唔使照顧個女咩？佢都知時日無多啦"},{"pid":"d50fedf32a31831015f632c88170dbf2e96b54ec","tid":125941,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9d9tjV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9d9tjV7.jpg&h=118a6421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/movie/M.1487092148.A.DDC.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fmovie%2FM.1487092148.A.DDC.html&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkrv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ec6c6910\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/movie/M.1487092148.A.DDC.html</a>"},{"pid":"7b9b40c7aabb3344df44e9ddada2349b9fb63e9f","tid":125941,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"話說,戲入面提到學識果D圓形文字就會學識預知能力<br />\n咁之後女主響大學教果D圓形文字,又出書<br />\n咁咪通街都預言者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7834a065ccf2c7100efc57e063b3eb6a125fa6e2","tid":125941,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說,戲入面提到學識果D圓形文字就會學識預知能力<br />\n咁之後女主響大學教果D圓形文字,又出書<br />\n咁咪通街都預言者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你估咁易咩"},{"pid":"a937d443153cebc19139b2ecc92fba877ac0df4c","tid":125941,"uid":15282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20